&lt;/ul></description></item><item><title>怎样提取PPT里的背景音乐</title><link>/archives/%E6%80%8E%E6%A0%B7%E6%8F%90%E5%8F%96ppt%E9%87%8C%E7%9A%84%E8%83%8C%E6%99%AF%E9%9F%B3%E4%B9%90/</link><pubDate>Wed, 17 Nov 2021 11:08:52 +0000</pubDate><guid>/archives/%E6%80%8E%E6%A0%B7%E6%8F%90%E5%8F%96ppt%E9%87%8C%E7%9A%84%E8%83%8C%E6%99%AF%E9%9F%B3%E4%B9%90/</guid><description>&lt;p>1.确保PPT扩展名为&lt;code>.pptx&lt;/code>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>2.将PPT扩展名改为&lt;code>.rar&lt;/code>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>3.用压缩软件打开，音乐文件在&lt;code>/ppt/media&lt;/code>文件夹下。&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>